PRODUCT BACKLOG

Books

US 01.01.01
As an owner, I want to add a book in my books, each denoted with a clear, suitable description (at least title, author, and ISBN) so that I can record the book.

Story point: 2
Risk Level: Low



US 01.02.01
As an owner, I want the book description by scanning it off the book (at least the ISBN) so that I obtain information about a book easily without manually entering the ISBN.

Story point: 8
Risk Level: High



US 01.03.01
As an owner or borrower, I want a book to have a status to be one of: available, requested, accepted, or borrowed so that I know which of my books are borrowed, requested and available.

Story point: 1
Risk Level: Low



US 01.04.01
As an owner, I want to view a list of all my books, and their descriptions, statuses, and current borrowers so that I see and interact with the books that interest me in my collection.

Story point: 1
Risk Level: Low





US 01.05.01
As an owner, I want to view a list of all my books, filtered by status so that I interact with or view all the books with the selected status.

Story point: 1
Risk Level: Low



US 01.06.01
As an owner, I want to view and edit a book description in my books so that I make desired changes and corrections to that record.

Story point: 2
Risk Level: Low



US 01.07.01
As an owner, I want to delete a book in my books so that I remove that book that I don’t want anymore from the list of records.

Story point: 2
Risk Level: Low




User profile

US 02.01.01
As an owner or borrower, I want a profile with a unique username and my contact information so that I have my own books and account that no one can else access.

Story point: 3
Risk Level: Medium



US 02.02.01
As an owner or borrower, I want to edit the contact information in my profile so that I keep my contact information up-to-date for interactions with other users.

Story point: 2
Risk Level: Low



US 02.03.01
As an owner or borrower, I want to retrieve and show the profile of a presented username so that I see the profiles of other users.

Story point: 3
Risk Level: Low



Searching

US 03.01.01
As a borrower, I want to specify a keyword, and search for all books that are not currently accepted or borrowed whose description contains the keyword so that I easily find available books.

Story point: 5
Risk Level: Medium



US 03.02.01
As a borrower, I want search results to show each book with its description, owner username, and status so that I see available books that interest me.

Story point: 1
Risk Level: Low



Requesting

US 04.01.01
As a borrower, I want to request a book that is not currently accepted or borrowed so that I alert the owner that I want to borrow that book.

Story point: 5
Risk Level: Medium



US 04.02.01
As a borrower, I want to view a list of books I have requested, each book with its description, owner username, and status so that I know which books I haven’t been able to borrow yet.

Story point: 3
Risk Level: Low



US 04.03.01
As an owner, I want to be notified of a request so that I know as soon as possible if someone wants to borrow one of my books.

Story point: 5
Risk Level: Medium



US 04.04.01
As an owner, I want to view all the requests on one of my books so that I know who wants to borrow my book.

Story point: 1
Risk Level: Low



Accepting

US 05.01.01
As an owner, I want to accept a request on one of my books so that I lend that book to some other user who requested it. (Any other requests on the book are declined.)

Story point: 1
Risk Level: Low



US 05.02.01
As an owner, I want to decline a request on one of my books so that I notify the one who requested it that I don’t want to lend it to him/her.

Story point: 1
Risk Level: Low



US 05.03.01
As a borrower, I want to be notified of an accepted request so that I can borrow the book as soon as possible

Story point: 5
Risk Level: Medium



US 05.04.01
As a borrower, I want to view a list of books I have requested that are accepted, each book with its description, and owner username so that I see all books I can proceed to borrow.

Story point: 1
Risk Level: Low



Borrowing

US 06.01.01
As an owner, I want to hand over a book by scanning the book ISBN code and denoting the book as borrowed so that I easily lend a book without manually entering the ISBN.

Story point: 8
Risk Level: High



US 06.02.01
As a borrower, I want to receive an accepted book by scanning the book ISBN code to confirm I have borrowed it so that I easily borrow a book without manually entering the ISBN.

Story point: 8
Risk Level: High



US 06.03.01
As a borrower, I want to view a list of books I am borrowing, each book with its description and owner username so that I see which books I was able to borrow. 

Story point: 1
Risk Level: Low



Returning

US 07.01.01
As a borrower, I want to hand over a book I borrowed by scanning the book ISBN code to denote the book as available so that I easily return a borrowed without manually entering the ISBN.

Story point: 8
Risk Level: High



US 07.02.01
As an owner, I want to receive a returned book by scanning the book ISBN code to confirm I have it available so that I easily receive a returned book without manually entering the ISBN.

Story point: 8
Risk Level: High



Photographs

US 08.01.01
As an owner, I want to optionally attach a photograph to a book of mine so that my book looks appealing.

Story point: 5
Risk Level: Medium



US 08.02.01
As an owner, I want to delete any attached photograph for a book of mine so that I remove an image I don’t like anymore.

Story Point: 5
Risk Level: Medium



US 08.03.01
As an owner or borrower, I want to view any attached photograph for a book so that I see more closely if a book is appealing or not by just looking at the image.

Story point: 5
Risk Level: Medium



Location

US 09.01.01
As an owner, I want to specify a geo location on a map of where to receive a book when I accept a request on the book so that the borrower knows where I want to hand over a requested book.

Story point: 13
Risk Level: High



US 09.02.01
As a borrower, I want to view the geo location of where to receive a book I will be borrowing so that I know where to meet the owner to receive the book.

Story point: 13
Risk Level: High
